<plot>Professor Vriendelijk has made a robot doll of used stuff and names it Pompy. He gives it to Migiel, an orphan child that helped him stopping his escaped lawn mower. Migiel is very happy with Pompy, but when Migiel gets other presents at his birthday, Pompy feels forgotten. Therefore Pompy decides to leave the orphanage to find other friends.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?438293</url></doc>
